Clarke Holds One-Stroke Lead in British Open

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-07-16T15:18:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-16/clarke-glover-share-1-stroke-lead-at-british-open-as-weather-dominates.html
Northern Ireland ’s Darren Clarke has
a one-stroke lead at 4-under par in the third round of the
British Open.  Clarke birdied the first hole at Royal St. George’s in
Sandwich,  England , before making bogey at the fifth.  Lucas
Glover , who shared the overnight lead with Clarke, bogeyed the
first hole to drop to 3-under. He’s tied for second with fellow
American  Dustin Johnson , who is 1-under par through eight holes.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  